Title

Source: R/cluster.R
cluster.Rd

Title

cluster(xy, extras = list())

Arguments

xy

Data frame.

extras

List of additional parameters. See Details.

Value

Factor.

Examples

df <- data.frame(
  x = rnorm(1000),
  y = rnorm(1000)
)
cluster(df)
